wdi-FM.AST.NFRG.CN.def: Net foreign assets are the sum of foreign assets held by monetary authorities and deposit money banks, less their foreign liabilities. Data are in current local currency.
wdi-FM.AST.NFRG.CN.name: Net foreign assets
wdi-FM.AST.NFRG.CN.source: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.
